text: Leah Ann Cevoli (born; May 4, 1974) is an American movie and television actress, host and producer. She first gained fame on the HBO series Deadwood and for providing voices on the Adult Swim series Robot Chicken. ==Other websites== * Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Philadelphia Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:American voice actors
